702902f-a.title: Brooklyn: 91st Street (East) - Schenck Avenue (North)
702902f-a.text:
(1)
East 91st Street, east side, north of Sghenck Ave; looking north-
east, and showing in the foreground Kavanagh's resort (1873), at ehat was
formerly known as Byrnes Point.
March 1925.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
MAY BE REPRODUCED.
(2)
The same, from a different angle.
June 1928.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
MAO BE RERODUCED.
